			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Yubikirira mu gico nk'uko intare yubikirira mu isenga ryayo, Yubikirira gufata umunyamubabaro, Kandi koko aramufata akamukururisha ikigoyi cye.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Yitugatuga yunamye, Intwari ze zitsinda abanyamubabaro.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Aribwira ati “Imana yibagiwe, Ihishe mu maso hayo ntabwo izabireba.”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Uwiteka haguruka, Mana manika ukuboko kwawe, Ntiwibagirwe umunyamubabaro.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Ni iki gituma umunyabyaha asuzugura Imana, Akayibwirira mu mutima we ati “Ntuzahōra”?",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Warabibonye kuko urebera igomwa n'urwango kubishyiraho ukuboko kwawe, Umunyamubabaro akwiringira wenyine, Ni wowe ujya utabara impfubyi.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Vunagura ukuboko k'umunyabyaha, Ushimikire ububi bw'umubi kugeza aho utazabumusanganira.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Uwiteka ni we Mwami iteka ryose, Abanyamahanga barimbukiye mu gihugu cye.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Uwiteka, wumvise ibyo abanyamubabaro bashaka, Uzakomeze imitima yabo, uzatyarize ugutwi,",
