			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Yohereza ijambo rye akabiyagisha, Ahuhisha umuyaga we amazi agatemba.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Amenyesha Abayakobo ijambo rye, Amenyesha Abisirayeli amategeko yandikishije n'amateka ye.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Nta rindi shyanga yagiriye atya, Amateka ye ntibayamenye. Haleluya."
